rows.label: tlk43400542_01_msg0002
rows.name: This is the best restaurant in Fons Maim, if I do say so myself.

rows.label: tlk43400542_01_msg0003
rows.name:
...Well, we get some drongos in here,
so it's more of a pub than anything...

rows.label: tlk43400542_01_msg0004
rows.name:
There are lots of places like this in
Fons Maim.

rows.label: tlk43400542_01_msg0005
rows.name:
All the mercs who get off duty come in
to eat and booze, and just have a laugh
and let their hair down.

rows.label: tlk43400542_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Also gives them a chance to talk about
their next assignments.

rows.label: tlk43400542_01_msg0007
rows.name: Well, hope you fit in here.
